    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_3_2576-2624",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2576-2624",
      "markText": "向我告别时，他紧握着我的双手说，他希望我也能活到他的岁数，因为每个年代虽有苦难，但也有它的美丽。",
      "totalCount": 480,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2576&rangeEnd=2624",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2576&rangeEnd=2624"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_5_3588-3627",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3588-3627",
      "markText": "如果女人的作用与男人在过去和现在起到的作用一样，那么，我不认为世界会变得更好。",
      "totalCount": 462,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3588&rangeEnd=3627",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3588&rangeEnd=3627"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_6_1405-1466",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1405-1466",
      "markText": "我不为我的命运承担任何责任；那是上帝的决定，如果你愿意这么想的话。但我要为我的性格负责，因为性格是可以塑造、净化和改善的。",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1405&rangeEnd=1466",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1405&rangeEnd=1466"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_3_1029-1082",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1029-1082",
      "markText": "齐格蒙特·鲍曼把自己的任务描述为将熟悉的事物变得陌生，将陌生的事物变得熟悉。他说，这也是社会学自身的任务。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1029&rangeEnd=1082",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1029&rangeEnd=1082"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_5_4243-4278",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4243-4278",
      "markText": "但她们没有把自己的劳动算进去。她们没有这样的观念，即她们的劳动也值钱。",
      "totalCount": 323,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4243&rangeEnd=4278",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4243&rangeEnd=4278"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_5_2807-2855",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2807-2855",
      "markText": "与常识相反，在爱的关系中，利他主义和利己主义的对立并非不可调和。它们会统一、融合，最终不分彼此。",
      "totalCount": 322,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2807&rangeEnd=2855",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2807&rangeEnd=2855"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_5_658-684",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "658-684",
      "markText": "消费者与商品之间的关系模式变成人与人之间的关系模式。",
      "totalCount": 320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=658&rangeEnd=684",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=658&rangeEnd=684"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_12_1307-1387",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1307-1387",
      "markText": "他们中的许多人已经失去了思考何为良好社会的能力。他们更喜欢思考怎样在这个无序的、不可预测的、让人不舒服的世界中，为自己，为家庭，为他们的亲人找到一个舒适的位置。",
      "totalCount": 320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1307&rangeEnd=1387",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1307&rangeEnd=1387"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_9_733-767",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "733-767",
      "markText": "思想始于异端，继而化作正统，最终止于迷信。这是历史上一切思想的命运。",
      "totalCount": 312,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=733&rangeEnd=767",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=733&rangeEnd=767"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_5_1117-1152",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1117-1152",
      "markText": "危险之处在于，关系模式的形式变了。人与人的关系，变成人与日用品的关系。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1117&rangeEnd=1152",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1117&rangeEnd=1152"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_9_4027-4054",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4027-4054",
      "markText": "消费社会使人难以幸福，因为它依赖的，就是我们的不幸福。",
      "totalCount": 294,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4027&rangeEnd=4054",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4027&rangeEnd=4054"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_5_2684-2779",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2684-2779",
      "markText": "如果爱的本性就是愿意站到你爱的对象那边，支持她，鼓励和赞美她，那么，情人就必须做好把自利放到第二位，放到被爱者之后的准备，就必须做好把自己的幸福当作次要问题，当作他者的幸福的附带问题的准备。",
      "totalCount": 280,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153003&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2684&rangeEnd=2779",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd232300813aba244g013400?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2684&rangeEnd=2779"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153003_5_2573-2609",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2573-2609",
      "markText": "如果你一直处在只对自己感兴趣的利己主义者的孤独之中，那它就是不可企及的。",
